Swedish: Vi är här för att hjälpa er med alla era frågor och behov
English UK: We're here to help you with all your questions and needs
English US: We're here to help you with all your questions and needs

Swedish: Skapa en ny beställning för dina kunder
English UK: Create a new order for your customers
English US: Create a new order for your customers

Swedish: Visa och spåra dina tidigare beställningar
English UK: View and track your previous orders
English US: View and track your previous orders

Swedish: så återkommer vi så snart som möjligt
English UK: and we'll get back to you as soon as possible
English US: and we'll get back to you as soon as possible

Swedish: Frågor om B8Shield produkter, priser eller leveranser hanteras via samma e-post
English UK: Questions about B8Shield products, prices or deliveries are handled via the same email
English US: Questions about B8Shield products, prices or deliveries are handled via the same email

Swedish: Behöver ni hjälp med portalen eller har tekniska frågor? Vi hjälper er gärna!
English UK: Need help with the portal or have technical questions? We're happy to help!
English US: Need help with the portal or have technical questions? We're happy to help!

Swedish: Ge butiksstället en synlig och central plats i butiken, gärna nära kassan.
English UK: Give the shop display a visible and central place in the shop, preferably near the checkout.
English US: Give the shop display a visible and central place in the shop, preferably near the checkout.

Swedish: Aktivt säljer och förklarar produkten för kunderna. Gör man inte det är sannolikheten stor att kunderna inte uppmärksammar produkten och därmed inte köper produkten vilket vare sig vi eller ni vinner på.
English UK: Actively sell and explain the product to customers. If you don't do this, there's a high probability that customers won't notice the product and therefore won't buy it, which benefits neither us nor you.
English US: Actively sell and explain the product to customers. If you don't do this, there's a high probability that customers won't notice the product and therefore won't buy it, which benefits neither us nor you.

Swedish: För att försäkra säljprocessen ytterligare skickar vi också med ett antal lösa B8Shields. Med fördel kan dessa läggas i en skål vid stället så att kund kan få klämma och känna på produkten.
English UK: To further ensure the sales process, we also send along a number of loose B8Shields. These can advantageously be placed in a bowl by the display so that customers can touch and feel the product.
English US: To further ensure the sales process, we also send along a number of loose B8Shields. These can advantageously be placed in a bowl by the display so that customers can touch and feel the product.

Swedish: När kunden dock väl förstår vad B8Shield är och gör, är den lätt att välja, men kunden måste förstå det först
English UK: When the customer understands what B8Shield is and does, it's easy to choose, but the customer must understand it first
English US: When the customer understands what B8Shield is and does, it's easy to choose, but the customer must understand it first

Swedish: B8Shield hindrar fiskedrag från att fastna i undervattensvegetation och andra undervattenshinder.
English UK: B8Shield prevents fishing lures from getting caught in underwater vegetation and other underwater obstacles.
English US: B8Shield prevents fishing lures from getting caught in underwater vegetation and other underwater obstacles.

English UK: B8Shield is available in 4 different variants:
English US: B8Shield is available in 4 different variants:

Swedish: B8Shield fästs på tre-krok. Passat till krokstorlek 2, 4 och 6, där storlek 2 också passar på krokstorlek 1. Krokstorlek 1/0 och 2/0 kommer inom kort.
English UK: B8Shield is attached to treble hooks. Fitted to hook sizes 2, 4 and 6, where size 2 also fits hook size 1. Hook sizes 1/0 and 2/0 coming soon.
English US: B8Shield is attached to treble hooks. Fitted to hook sizes 2, 4 and 6, where size 2 also fits hook size 1. Hook sizes 1/0 and 2/0 coming soon.

Swedish: B8Shields är designad så att man enkelt kan växla den mellan olika drag vid behov.
English UK: B8Shield is designed so that you can easily switch it between different lures as needed.
English US: B8Shield is designed so that you can easily switch it between different lures as needed.

Swedish: Nej, B8Shield påverkar inte krokens förmåga att kroka fisk. Under ett bett flexar sköldens vingar för att exponera krokarna, vilket säkerställer en lyckad fångst. Du krokar helt enkelt fisken som vanligt.
English UK: No, B8Shield does not affect the hook's ability to hook fish. During a bite, the shield's wings flex to expose the hooks, ensuring a successful catch. You simply hook the fish as normal.
English US: No, B8Shield does not affect the hook's ability to hook fish. During a bite, the shield's wings flex to expose the hooks, ensuring a successful catch. You simply hook the fish as normal.

English UK: Question 1: Will the fish stop biting?
English US: Question 1: Will the fish stop biting?

Swedish: Nej, B8Shield är testad med många typer av drag. Ingen skillnad i gång.
English UK: No, B8Shield is tested with many types of lures. No difference in action.
English US: No, B8Shield is tested with many types of lures. No difference in action.

Swedish: Fråga 2: Förstör det gången på draget?
English UK: Question 2: Does it ruin the action of the lure?
English US: Question 2: Does it ruin the action of the lure?

Swedish: När du fiskar där det finns många undervattenhinder som ex. undervattensvegetation eller där det är stenigt, alltså där fisken ofta gömmer sig.
English UK: When you fish where there are many underwater obstacles such as underwater vegetation or where it's rocky, i.e. where fish often hide.
English US: When you fish where there are many underwater obstacles such as underwater vegetation or where it's rocky, i.e. where fish often hide.

Swedish: Fråga 3: När ska man använda den?
English UK: Question 3: When should you use it?
English US: Question 3: When should you use it?

Swedish: Vanliga frågor – och vad du svarar:
English UK: Common questions – and what you answer:
English US: Common questions – and what you answer:

Swedish: Visa och spåra dina tidigare beställningar
English UK: View and track your previous orders
English US: View and track your previous orders

Swedish: Kunderna vet därför inte ännu vad B8Shield är eller vilket problem den löser, och därför söker man således inte aktivt efter B8Shield trots att man har problemet med att fastna
English UK: Customers therefore don't yet know what B8Shield is or what problem it solves, and therefore don't actively search for B8Shield despite having the problem
English US: Customers therefore don't yet know what B8Shield is or what problem it solves, and therefore don't actively search for B8Shield despite having the problem

Swedish: B8Shield är en ny och unik produkt som löser ett vanligt problem för fiskare - att fastna i undervattensvegetation och andra undervattenshinder.
English UK: B8Shield is a new and unique product that solves a common problem for anglers - getting caught in underwater vegetation and other underwater obstacles.
English US: B8Shield is a new and unique product that solves a common problem for anglers - getting caught in underwater vegetation and other underwater obstacles.

Swedish: B8Shield är samtidigt en helt ny typ av både produkt och produktkategori.
English UK: B8Shield is also a completely new type of both product and product category.
English US: B8Shield is also a completely new type of both product and product category.

English UK: For this reason it is crucial that you:
English US: For this reason it is crucial that you:

Swedish: När du skall natt fiska och vill attrahera fiskar i grumliga eller mörka vatten.
English UK: When you're night fishing and want to attract fish in murky or dark waters.
English US: When you're night fishing and want to attract fish in murky or dark waters.

Swedish: När man skall fiska i stark solljus hjälper dess gnistrande färg till med att attrahera mer fisk.
English UK: When fishing in strong sunlight, its sparkling colour helps attract more fish.
English US: When fishing in strong sunlight, its sparkling color helps attract more fish.

Swedish: Utnyttja den traditionella röda färgen på många betesfiskar för att attrahera mer fisk.
English UK: Utilise the traditional red colour of many baitfish to attract more fish.
English US: Utilize the traditional red color of many baitfish to attract more fish.

Swedish: När man inte vill kompromissa med fiskedragets naturliga färger och utseende.
English UK: When you don't want to compromise the natural colours and appearance of the fishing lure.
